{"type":"message","id":"4015dffe","parentId":"e9735b1a","timestamp":"2026-03-31T09:05:50.833Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Tue 2026-03-31 11:05 GMT+2] I installed nvm and used nvm v.22 to install qmd because it didn't work with node v.25. Should I try to restart the computer first or something basic?"}],"timestamp":1774947950830}}
{"type":"message","id":"dc18b5cb","parentId":"4015dffe","timestamp":"2026-03-31T09:05:59.125Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Restarting the computer probably won’t fix this by itself.\n\nWhat’s happening is more specific: **QMD was built under Node 22, but something is currently trying to run it under Node 25**. A reboot won’t change that unless your startup environment also changes which `node` gets used.\n\nBest “basic” checks, in order:\n\n1. **Check which Node OpenClaw is actually using**\n   - `node -v`\n   - `which node`\n\n2. **Check which Node QMD is using when launched from the same environment**\n   - If QMD is a global package under nvm’s Node 22, it may only work when that Node 22 environment is active.\n\n3. **Restart just the relevant service/process**\n   - If OpenClaw or the memory service was started before you switched Node versions, restart that process first.\n   - A service restart is more useful than a full machine reboot here.\n\nWhy I’d avoid reboot-first:\n- If your shell loads `nvm` but the service/GUI app does **not**, the machine will come back up and still use the wrong Node.\n- Native module mismatch errors almost always mean **wrong runtime version**, not “needs a reboot”.\n\nWhat I’d do:\n- First verify whether the backend process is on **Node 22 or 25**\n- Then restart OpenClaw from an environment where **Node 22 is active**, if QMD still depends on 22\n\nIf you want, I can help you check the current Node/runtime paths and tell you the exact next step.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ab9e364ba0e4e510069cb8e6ff884819591f9697f906dacc4\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":11374,"output":329,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11703,"cost":{"input":0.028435000000000002,"output":0.004935,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.033370000000000004}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774947950834,"responseId":"resp_0ab9e364ba0e4e510069cb8e6f386c81959069757cdd90795f"}}
